===Etymology===
From {{MF.}} {{term|turkeis|lang=fr}}, from {{OF.}} {{term|turqueise||Turkish|lang=fr}}. The stone was originally brought to Europe from [[w:Turkestan|Turkestan]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A sky-blue, greenish-blue, or greenish-gray semi-precious gemstone.
# A pale [[green]]ish-[[blue]] [[color|colour]], like that of the gemstone.
